<item>
            <title>[DERBY-4022] Remove dependency of junit targets on deprecated jdk16 variable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4022</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The junit target for running the jdbc4 tests depends on the jdk16 variable being set in your ant.properties. For the build, this variable has been deprecated. We should be able to make the jdbc4 tests depend on whether the environment is Java 6 instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
